"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US military reports another death a day after two of its soldiers were killed in Jordan. The Crown Prosecution Service says it has requested their extradition from the US, while their lawyer says they are innocent.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Military Deaths\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ej\u00e9rcito de EE.UU. informa otra muerte un d\u00eda despu\u00e9s de que dos de sus soldados murieran en Jordania. El Servicio de Fiscal\u00eda de la Corona dice que ha pedido su extradici\u00f3n de EE.UU., mientras que su abogado dice que son inocentes.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Muertes en el Ej\u00e9rcito de EE.UU.\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Fifteen children are among 67 people rescued, officials say, with dozens still missing. The latest update from the US Food and Drug Administration means the exact source of the parasite is still not known.\",            \"english_title\": \"Children Rescued\",            \"translated_version\": \"Quince ni\u00f1os est\u00e1n entre 67 personas rescatadas, dicen los oficiales, con docenas a\u00fan desaparecidas. La \u00faltima actualizaci\u00f3n de la Administraci\u00f3n de Alimentos y Medicamentos de EE.UU. significa que la fuente exacta del par\u00e1sito a\u00fan no se conoce.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ni\u00f1os Rescatados\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Eight people die and dozens are injured as several cities are hit by missile and drone attacks, while Kyiv continues its own assault on Russian infrastructure.\",            \"english_title\": \"Missile Attacks\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ocho personas mueren y docenas est\u00e1n heridas cuando varias ciudades son atacadas por misiles y drones, mientras Kyiv contin\u00faa su propio ataque a la infraestructura rusa.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataques con Misiles\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The artwork in the capital Oslo was unveiled on Sunday ahead of the 15th anniversary of the attack.\",            \"english_title\": \"Oslo Artwork\",            \"translated_version\": \"La obra de arte en la capital Oslo fue presentada el domingo antes del 15 aniversario del ataque.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Obra de Arte en Oslo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"He was arrested in 2021 during Cuba's largest anti-government protests in decades and spent five years in prison.\",            \"english_title\": \"Cuban Protests\",            \"translated_version\": \"Fue arrestado en 2021 durante las mayores protestas antigubernamentales en Cuba en d\u00e9cadas y pas\u00f3 cinco a\u00f1os en prisi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Protestas en Cuba\"        }    ]}"